Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,features that fundamentally change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.21,0:01:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,how we learn and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,research.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the game changer M
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,deep research.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This feature is essentially
